"a systemwide location.  The resulting profile will get used when\n"
"the RANDR plug-in gets run in mate-settings-daemon.\n"
"\n"
"SOURCE_FILE - a full pathname, typically /home/username/.config/"
"monitors.xml\n"
"\n"
